    "name": "死而符生",
    "steam_appid": 3073990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《死而符生》是一款将老虎机玩法和牌组构建相结合的Roguelite游戏。在这片被绝望侵蚀的大地上，你将持有多本符文秘典，操纵符文匹配连接以击败敌人。搭配好各类遗物，用惊天动地的大数字碾碎那些腐朽的黑暗爪牙。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >匹配元素符文</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就像操控一台魔法驱动的老虎机。通过保留符文，重新随机等方式尽可能的连接更多同元素符文，打出高额伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每本符文书会有不同的链路刻印，处于链路节点上的符文更为关键，明智选择每次施法的时机，才能在不断增强的敌人面前屡战屡胜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/ed75aa80dfbb7a53c9978187184ad941.poster.avif?t=1771534244\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/ed75aa80dfbb7a53c9978187184ad941.webm?t=1771534244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构筑符文秘典</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过以下方式增加匹配符文的机会在独特的牌组构建体验中自定义法术书中的符文列。添加、移除和每本符文书都包含五个符文列，每一列相当于单独的牌库。在商人伙伴的助力下，添加、移除或修改不同符文列，让每次重随更贴近你的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素符文还可以附加光环和项链来强化，匹配连接后，链路上每个符文的基础和额外效果会逐个触发。耐心规划，一次施法中甚至可以重复触发，累积优势进而锁定胜局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/eca6d8092ba4ffe09fc7ca748a3f8f2d.poster.avif?t=1771534244\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/eca6d8092ba4ffe09fc7ca748a3f8f2d.webm?t=1771534244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集海量饰品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集和搭配各类饰品是本作的重中之重。探索 150 余种饰品，发掘它们的协同效果和疯狂组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >饰品的带来的提升多种多样，提高伤害和倍率，符文触发次数，更强的随机性掌控，甚至让不同元素的符文互相匹配。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/81443c930a61ff2141b3d86f3b775730.poster.avif?t=1771534244\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/81443c930a61ff2141b3d86f3b775730.webm?t=1771534244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迎战随机敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗开始时，可以在三个不同敌人之间做出选择。特质强大的敌人意味着更丰厚的奖励，但简单的敌人也许带着诡异的赐福。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/58046a7e8be7b4ac2dc42fd33ab062e1.poster.avif?t=1771534244\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073990/extras/58046a7e8be7b4ac2dc42fd33ab062e1.webm?t=1771534244\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅如此，不同敌人也对应着不同的商店类型，可以在战前选择中预览，每次选择都将不同程度改变构筑走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《死而符生》目前包含数百种可选内容，确保每次冒险都是独一无二，在千万条道路上击溃来自黑暗的爪牙。</p>",
